Directions
From Route 295, take exit 7 (Franklin Arterial) onto Franklin Arterial and  head up the hill towards downtown Portland. At the fourth set of lights,  take a right onto Congress Street. Go through one light, and turn left at  the next light onto Temple Street. Go straight through the first  intersection. Two City Center will be on your right with a blue awning.
The Temple Street Parking garage is directly across the street on your  left. We are able to validate two hours of parking at any city garage.


