Directions:
From Route 95, take Exit 7 (Portsmouth Downtown) and head towards downtown  Portsmouth.  You will pass the Sheraton Hotel on the right where the road  jogs slightly to the left and up a hill.  You will come to a stop sign  where you will continue to go straight for a short distance which will  bring you into Market Square.  Once in Market Square (also known as  Congress Street), the old North Church will be on your left.  Eighteen  Congress Street’s entrance is located between Popovers (the next building  after old North Church) and Kilwins.  Take the elevator to  the second floor and Vigilant Capital Management’s office is straight off  the elevator.
Also there is the Hanover/High Street Parking garage located a couple of  blocks from the office.  If you bring in your ticket from the parking garage, we will validate it.














